alerts.title: Flood Warning
alerts.description: ...A FLOOD WARNING FOR A DAM FLOODGATE RELEASE REMAINS IN EFFECT UNTIL 300 AM MST TUESDAY FOR MARICOPA COUNTY... At 246 AM MST, Salt River Project continued to release water from Granite Reef Dam. Elevated flow down the Salt River has forced the closure of roads built in the river channel between Granite Reef Dam and Tempe Town Lake.
